"@trashboat":/dis/the-time-wasting-thread/post/5375390e6368720f72790300#post_5375390e6368720f72790300
Intersex is a umbrella terminology.

Someone somewhere went, "This is too fucking complicated" and came up with a umbrella terminology and went, "ahhh screw it; here's a general terminology to describe all these groups".

In other words:  If you like traps there's a pretty decent chances that you're bisexual; not a 100% chance, but a still pretty good chance none the less.
